long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Generate tokens for use with token-enabled applications so you can have full access to your live events!

Sometimes it happens that APIs provided by third parties for live events fail and this is a problem for a content creator who needs their tools on the fly!

That's why this extension allows you to never be disconnected from your live even if third party APIs may fail this extension won't!
